# Kyokai Standard Library Licensing

Kyokai-owned standard library files are licensed under:

```text
SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later WITH GCC-exception-3.1
```

The exception allows ordinary Kyokai target programs to link against and use the standard library without that fact alone forcing the user's whole program under the GPL.

Full license texts are available at the repository root:

- `../COPYING`
- `../COPYING.RUNTIME`

Inherited Austral files may still carry Apache-2.0 or Apache-2.0 WITH LLVM-exception notices. Preserve those notices until the files are replaced or relicensed by the relevant copyright holder.
